{"tid":629023,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"大家傳波射波嘅時候係望住個波定個目標","createTime":"2018-04-14T11:04:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T13:04:39.000Z","uid":135178,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"33851797fd848f15a916008b0fd0fd1c1fce1c86","tid":629023,"uid":135178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T11:04:57.000Z","msg":"之前睇過啲教學話傳波射波嘅時候應該要望住個波，咁先可以確保你踢得中同踢得應<br />\n<br />\n但係當我只望住波嘅時候，傳/射都會歪左，係抬起頭傳/射先會準啲，但有時又會撻Q<br />\n<br />\n最好方法係咪先抬頭望，傳/射嗰刻再望個波?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd86a8d38b23e7e2a8e210655033fef467d4d248","tid":629023,"uid":134235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T11:05:48.000Z","msg":"我係望兩者中間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a34182b32d338f9ecda309b552b1e404f5dc1c42","tid":629023,"uid":51604,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T11:07:53.000Z","msg":"望目標好易比人睇穿去截<br />\n但可以利用呢點 望左走右fake人"},{"pid":"4ab98ab44b8442028b9fca829ae1d1b0f4246920","tid":629023,"uid":135178,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T11:13:28.000Z","msg":"同埋帶波扭波去到一流嘅水平，係咪可以用隻腳代替隻眼去感應個波?<br />\n<br />\n但係睇片美斯過人嘅時候望緊嘅都係介乎個波同對面球員隻腳嘅角度<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://apasport.az/upload/images/news/2017/november/07/big/77f88c152e61bd1c424583a498b78d41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fapasport.az%2Fupload%2Fimages%2Fnews%2F2017%2Fnovember%2F07%2Fbig%2F77f88c152e61bd1c424583a498b78d41.jpg&h=b71fed67&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ccb0c5a4499dfc2f66f55487bbbf0d4584495ea","tid":629023,"uid":43015,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4ab98ab44b8442028b9fca829ae1d1b0f4246920","tid":629023,"uid":135178,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T11:13:28.000Z","msg":"同埋帶波扭波去到一流嘅水平，係咪可以用隻腳代替隻眼去感應個波?<br />\n<br />\n但係睇片美斯過人嘅時候望緊嘅都係介乎個波同對面球員隻腳嘅角度<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://apasport.az/upload/images/news/2017/novemb